@startuml
[*] --> PowerOnCheck
PowerOnCheck --> PowerOnCheck : problem detected
PowerOnCheck --> ReadyToUse : everything fine
ReadyToUse --> Reset : reset system
ReadyToUse --> Activate : activate system
ReadyToUse --> TurnOff : turn off system
ReadyToUse --> Monitoring : start monitoring
Monitoring --> AlarmActivated : sensor triggered
AlarmActivated --> SendingAlerts : send alerts
SendingAlerts --> Monitoring : continue monitoring
Monitoring --> ReadyToUse : false alarm or time ends
ReadyToUse --> [*] : enter password
@enduml
